msgstr "TSIG non-standard."

#: lib/Domain/Service/DnsValidation/TSIGRecordValidator.php:338
msgid "RFC 8945 recommends using HMAC-SHA256 as the standard TSIG algorithm."
msgstr "RFC 8945: HMAC-SHA256."

