"corresponding DNSKEY record."
msgstr "DS trust."

#: lib/Domain/Service/DnsValidation/CSYNCRecordValidator.php:96
msgid ""
"CSYNC records should only be placed at the zone apex (RFC 7477). This record "
"may not be processed by parental agents."
msgstr "CSYNC apex."

